g.text: Connections align with Adafruit STM32F405 Feather as much as possible for compatibility
Fused input with reverse polarity protection, fereite bead for HF interference
Can be removed if required, as MCU has internal oscillator.
An external oscillator will be more precise.
Capacitor values need to be determined based on crystal chosen
Uses I2C for communication (Adafruit has library support)
VDDIO should be powered up before VDD
Interrupt may need to be connected depending on later decisions
Uses same pinout as Adafruit STM32F4 Feather for compatibility
